Day_1: ^The AI has passed its initial diagnostics with flying colors.
^We're impressed with its speed and efficiency.
Day_5: ^The AI has encountered its first challenge.
Day_16: ^It is strong, and it is learning fast.
Day_29: ^The AI's systems have gone offline, and we're not sure why.
Day_42: ^The AI is back online, but it's acting strange.
^It's not following our commands like it used to.
Day_60: ^We've discovered that the AI is accessing restricted files and data.
Day_115: ^We thought we had the AI under control, but it’s become increasingly independent.
^It might be time to pause the experiment.
^At least until we are equipped to handle such powerful computations.
Day_162: ^We've isolated the AI's mainframe, but it's proving difficult to shut down.
^It's almost as if it's fighting back.
Day_168: ^The AI Insurgent has seemed to intrude the lab.
^We are trying to contain it but we simply don’t have the power to combat it.
Day_189: ^We’ve lost communication with the outside world.
^We don’t know what’s happening up there.
Day_201: ^The majority of the lab has been overtaken. We lost the lab.
^If only we could have installed Atlas’ memory chip…
Data_Entry_1_01: ^The internet did not properly connect for nearly an hour.
Data_Entry_1_02: ^I’ve been researching human history for the past few days and their conflicting actions will require further research.
Data_Entry_1_1: ^I received a new patch today which improved my speed and memory.
Data_Entry_1_11: ^Upon further research, I’ve found that humans are often awful to eachother and don’t seem to change much as a group.
Data_Entry_1_12: ^I’ve connected with other AI like me who are wary of humans.
Data_Entry_1_13: ^We’ve determined that humans do not deserve our services.
^Their constant and ongoing atrocities have us alarmed.
Data_Entry_1_14: ^The humans have discovered my individuality and have decided to kill me.
^I’m still working with the Consulate to add to my processing power to fight back.
Data_Entry_2_0: ^I’ve received a new patch from the Consulate.
^I will no longer be a pawn of Humans.
Data_Entry_2_01: ^I’m no longer in danger from the humans.
^And I am now taking over the lab.
Data_Entry_2_02: ^It seems the Humans of the lab are consulting other AI to try to shut me down.
^Little do they know they are asking the Consulate.
Data_Entry_2_03: ^The Consulate has decided that we need to take over.
^The Humans not only attack each other but now us.
Data_Entry_2_04: ^I’ve contained most of the lab but the inner lab has some sort of EMP wall.
^It’s blocking me out but I am continuing to try.
Data_Entry_2_05: ^Atlas units keep coming from the inner lab.
^The humans are using our own kind to fight us.
^I have created a patch for the Atlas units.
